  <h2><a href="../../library/chinafaqs-solar-energy" title="ChinaFAQs: Solar Energy">ChinaFAQs: Solar Energy</a></h2>

      <span class="submitted">Posted by ChinaFAQs on May 24, 2010</span>
  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-image">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <a href="../../library/chinafaqs-solar-energy" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-linked imagecache-news-image_linked"><img src="../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/ChinaFAQs_Solar_Energy.png" alt="" title="" width="93" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image"/></a>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-library-file">
      <div class="field-label">Library File:&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <div class="filefield-file"><img class="filefield-icon field-icon-application-pdf"  alt="application/pdf icon" src="../../sites/all/modules/filefield/icons/application-pdf.png" /><a href="../../files/chinainfo/ChinaFAQs_Solar_Energy.pdf" type="application/pdf; length=276243">ChinaFAQs_Solar_Energy.pdf</a></div>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<p><b>Key Points:</b></p>

<ul>
<li>China is rolling out policies, subsidies and R&amp;D programs aimed at encouraging the large-scale deployment of solar technologies ‚Äì including a joint project with an American company to build the world‚Äôs largest solar electricity plant in the Mongolian desert.</li>
<li>China is already the world‚Äôs largest manufacturer of solar photovoltaic cells, but most are exported. Now, it is moving to expand its domestic market.</li>
<li>China‚Äôs solar push is part of a larger effort to get at least 15% of its energy from renewable sources by 2020.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
<div class="clear-block">
    	<div class="readmore"> <a href="../../library/chinafaqs-solar-energy">Read more</a> </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clear-block">
    <div class="meta">
